Thermal processing panel - viewer and analyzer of radiometric images.
Most files generated by Flir and Irtis infrared cameras are supported.

Features include: temperature compensation recalculation, rescaling, zoom based
on nearest interpolation or realsr algorithms, HD scale, 14 palettes created
from svg files, histogram, line profile, image overlays for highlighting,
level slices, temperature-dependant grown highlights, export images to png
files, export plots to gnuplot scripts.
